Main cyrillic facets realisations

unicyr_ctype.hpp - Unicode cyrillic ctype facet
ctype_cp1251.hpp - CP1251 codepage ctype facet for cyrillic
codecvt/codecvt_cp1251.hpp - windows-1251 <-> UTF-8 codecvt facet
codecvt/codecvt_cp866.hpp - ibm-866 <-> UTF-8 codecvt facet


test.cpp - test suite for codecvt (need BOOST_TEST_FRAMEWORK), use
Makefile.mingw (for Windows MinGW) and Makefile for building.
